title: Ep 126 - The Canadian Caesar
description: Todd, Digs, Nick, Connor, Gump, Bailey and Zito catch you up on what the weekend had in store for each of them. Gump rescheduled his flight so they took advantage of him being in studio by talking a little about Canada and the weird stuff they drink. Another shootin’ the shit and lettin’ it rip episode to brighten to your day and make you just a little bit dumber than you were before.
